::Ramulus::

Ramulus looks at Fliq, nodding. "Yeah, I'm totaly fine," he says, his lips 
tightening as his stomach turns, "Just not very used to this," he says, 
turning a bit white again.

He sits back in his chair, "I'll be fine. This is the first time I ever left 
earth."
